                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020714-37-off196 t18020714-37-cd197"></join>, a waistcoat, value 2s. a shirt, value 4s. two handkerchiefs, value 3s. a hat, value 6s. a jacket, value 7s. a pair of breeches, value 5s. a quart of Hollands, value 3s. and a glass bottle, value 3d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
